text: Lake Placid 3 is a 2010 American made-for-television horror comedy movie directed by Griff Furst. It is a sequel to Lake Placid 2 (2007). It is the third installment in the Lake Placid movie series. The movie premiered on August 21, 2010, on Syfy.
